import numpy as np

import statsmodels.api as sm

Tnh Dng/Khng Dng

Mt gi nh thng khng c kim tra trong phn tch chui thi gian l tnh dng ca d liu. D liu c coi l dng khi cc tham s ca qu trnh sinh d liu khng thay i theo thi gian. V d, hy xem xt hai chui, A v B. Chui A c to ra t mt qu trnh dng vi cc tham s c nh, trong khi chui B c sinh ra vi cc tham s thay i theo thi gian.

In[2]:
def generate_datapoint(params):
    mu = params[0]
    sigma = params[1]
    return np.random.normal(mu, sigma)

Chui A

In[3]:
# Set the parameters and the number of datapoints
params = (0, 1)
T = 100

A = pd.Series(index=range(T), dtype='float64')
A.name = 'A'

for t in range(T):
    A[t] = generate_datapoint(params)

plt.plot(A)
plt.xlabel('Time')
plt.ylabel('Value')
plt.legend(['Series A']);

Chui B

# Set the number of datapoints
T = 100

B = pd.Series(index=range(T), dtype="float64")
B.name = 'B'

for t in range(T):
    # Now the parameters are dependent on time
    # Specifically, the mean of the series changes over time
    params = (t * 0.1, 1)
    B[t] = generate_datapoint(params)

plt.plot(B)
plt.xlabel('Time')
plt.ylabel('Value')
plt.legend(['Series B']);

Ti Sao Tnh Khng Dng L Nguy Him

Nhiu bi kim tra thng k, su trong cc iu kin gi nh ca chng, yu cu rng d liu c kim tra phi l dng. Ngoi ra, nu bn s dng mt cch ngy th mt s thng k trn mt tp d liu khng dng, bn s nhn c kt qu khng hp l. V d, hy xem xt vic ly trung bnh qua d liu khng dng $B$ ca chng ta.

Gi tr trung bnh c tnh ton s cho thy gi tr trung bnh ca tt c cc im d liu, nhng s khng hu ch cho bt k d on no v trng thi tng lai. N tr nn v ngha khi so snh vi bt k thi im c th no, v l mt tp hp cc trng thi khc nhau ti cc thi im khc nhau c trn ln vi nhau. y ch l mt v d n gin v r rng v vic ti sao tnh khng n nh c th gy rc ri cho phn tch, v nhng vn tinh vi hn c th pht sinh trong thc t.

Kim tra Tnh dng

By gi chng ta mun kim tra tnh dng bng cch s dng mt bi kim tra thng k.

In[6]:
def check_for_stationarity(X, cutoff=0.01):
    # H_0 in adfuller is unit root exists (non-stationary)
    # We must observe significant p-value to convince ourselves that the series is stationary
    pvalue = adfuller(X)[1]
    if pvalue < cutoff:
        print('p-value = ' + str(pvalue) + ' The series ' + X.name +' is likely stationary.')
        return True
    else:
        print('p-value = ' + str(pvalue) + ' The series ' + X.name +' is likely non-stationary.')
        return False

Th t Tch hp (Integration)

i din Trung bnh ng / nh l Wold

Mt khi nim quan trng trong phn tch chui thi gian l i din trung bnh ng.

i din ny biu th bt k chui thi gian no $Y_t$ nh sau:

$$Y_t = \sum_{j=0}^\infty b_j \epsilon_{t-j} + \eta_t$$

  • $\epsilon$ l chui 'i mi'
  • $b_j$ l trng s trung bnh ng ca chui i mi
  • $\eta$ l mt chui xc nh

iu quan trng y nh sau. $\eta$ l xc nh, chng hn nh mt sng sine. Do , chng ta c th m hnh ha n mt cch hon ho. Quy trnh i mi l ngu nhin v c mt m phng thng tin mi xy ra theo thi gian. C th, $\epsilon_t = \hat Y_t - Y_t$ trong $\hat Y_t$ l d on ti u ca $Y_t$ ch s dng thng tin t thi gian trc $t$. Ni cch khc, d on tt nht m bn c th thc hin ti thi im $t-1$ khng th tnh n s ngu nhin trong $\epsilon$.

Mi $b_j$ ch ra mc nh hng ca cc gi tr trc ca $\epsilon$ n $Y_t$.

Quay li Th t Tch hp

Chng ta s ghi ch th t tch hp-i l $I(i)$.

Mt chui thi gian c cho l $I(0)$ nu iu kin sau y c tha mn trong mt i din trung bnh ng. Ni mt cch n gin, t tng quan ca chui suy gim nhanh.

$$\sum_{k=0}^\infty |b_k|^2 < \infty$$

Tnh cht ny ha ra ng vi tt c cc chui dng, nhng t n khng gi cho chui dng. iu ny c ngha l trng thi dng suy ra $I(0)$, nhng $I(0)$ khng suy ra trng thi dng. bit thm v cc th t tch hp, vui lng xem cc lin kt sau.

  • https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Order_of_integration
  • https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wold%27s_theorem

Kim tra cho $I(0)$

Trong thc t, vic kim tra xem tng ca cc t tng quan c hu hn hay khng c th khng kh thi. iu ny c th trong mt php suy din ton hc, nhng khi chng ta c mt tp d liu hu hn v mt s lng c lng t tng quan hu hn, tng s lun hu hn. Vi kh khn ny, cc bi kim tra cho $I(0)$ da vo trng thi dng suy ra tnh cht. Nu chng ta pht hin rng mt chui l dng, th n cng phi l $I(0)$.

Hy xem xt chui A ban u ca chng ta (chui dng). Bi v A l chui dng, chng ta bit rng n cng l $I(0)$.

In[10]:

plt.ylabel('Value')
plt.legend(['Series A']);

Xy dng cc bc tch hp mt cch quy np

Nu ta ly mt chui $I(0)$ v tnh tng tch ly ca n (tch phn ri rc), chui mi s l $I(1)$. Lu rng iu ny lin quan n khi nim tch phn trong gii tch. Mi quan h tng t cng p dng chung, c c $I(n)$, ta ly mt chui $I(0)$ v thc hin vic tnh tng tch ly lp li $n$ ln.

By gi, hy to mt chui $I(1)$ bng cch ly tng tch ly ca A.

Phn Tch Cp Tch Hp

Ngc li, tm cp tch hp ca mt chui cho trc, chng ta thc hin php ton ngc ca tng tch ly, l hm khc bit $\Delta$ hoc khc bit theo tng mc. C th l

$$(1-L) X_t = X_t - X_{t-1} = \Delta X$$

$$(1-L)^d X_t$$

Trong trng hp ny, $L$ l ton t tr. i khi cng c vit l $B$ ch 'li li'. $L$ ly cc phn t th hai n cui trong mt chui thi gian, v $L^k$ ly cc phn t th k n cui. V vy

$$L X_t = X_{t-1}$$

v

$$(1-L) X_t = X_t - X_{t-1}$$

Mt chui $Y_t$ c gi l $I(1)$ nu $Y_t - Y_{t-1}$ l $I(0)$. Ni cch khc, nu bn ly mt chui $I(0)$ v tnh tng tch ly ca n, bn s nhn c mt chui $I(1)$.

iu Cn Nh Quan Trng

Khi tt c cc php ton c thc hin, hy nh rng bt k chui no dng cng u l $I(0)$.

D liu thc

Hy th nghim iu ny vi mt s d liu gi thc t.

GHI CH QUAN TRNG

Nh mi khi, bn khng nn ngy th gi nh rng v mt chui thi gian l dng trong qu kh th n s tip tc l dng trong tng lai. Cc th nghim kim tra tnh nht qun ca tnh dng nh kim tra cho v kim tra ngoi mu l cn thit. iu ny ng vi bt k thuc tnh thng k no, chng ti ch nhc li y. Li tc cng c th vo v ra khi trng thi dng, v c th l dng hoc khng dng ty thuc vo khung thi gian v tn sut ly mu.

Lu : Phn tch Li sut

L do li sut thng c s dng trong m hnh ha ti chnh nh lng l v chng c tnh n nh cao hn so vi gi c. iu ny lm cho vic m hnh ha chng d dng hn v vic d on li sut tr nn kh thi hn. D on gi c th kh khn hn, v c nhiu xu hng do s tch hp $I(1)$ ca chng. Ngay c vic s dng m hnh d on li sut d on gi cng c th gp kh khn, v bt k sai st no trong d on li sut s c phng i theo thi gian.

ng tch hp (Cointegration)

Chng ta tho lun v tnh dng v bc tch hp, by gi chng ta c th ni v ng tch hp.

nh ngha: T hp tuyn tnh

Mt t hp tuyn tnh ca cc chui thi gian ($X_1$, $X_2$, $\dots$, $X_k$) l mt chui thi gian mi $Y$ c xy dng nh sau cho bt k tp hp no ca cc s thc $b_1 \dots b_k$:

$$Y = b_1X_1 + b_2X_2 + \dots + b_kX_k$$

nh ngha chnh thc

nh ngha chnh thc v ng tch hp l nh sau.

i vi mt tp hp cc chui thi gian ($X_1$, $X_2$, $\dots$, $X_k$), nu tt c cc chui u l $I(1)$, v mt s t hp tuyn tnh ca chng l $I(0)$, chng ta ni rng tp hp cc chui thi gian ny l ng tch hp.

V d

$X_1$, $X_2$, v $X_3$ u l $I(1)$, v $2X_1 + X_2 + 0X_3 = 2X_1 + X_2$ l $I(0)$. Trong trng hp ny, cc chui thi gian l ng tch hp.

Trc gic

Trc gic y l i vi mt t hp tuyn tnh no ca cc chui, kt qu thiu nhiu t hip phng sai v ch yu l nhiu. iu ny rt hu ch cho cc trng hp nh giao dch cp, trong chng ta tm hai ti sn c gi c ng tch hp. V t hp tuyn tnh ca gi c ca chng $b_1A_1 + b_2A_2$ l nhiu, chng ta c th t cc vo mi quan h $b_1A_1 + b_2A_2$ s quay v gi tr trung bnh v thc hin cc giao dch theo . Xem Bi ging Giao dch Cp bit thm thng tin.

V d D liu M phng

Hy to mt s d liu minh ha iu ny.

In[19]:
# Length of series
N = 100

# Generate a stationary random X1
X1 = np.random.normal(0, 1, N)
# Integrate it to make it I(1)
X1 = np.cumsum(X1)
X1 = pd.Series(X1)
X1.name = 'X1'

# Make an X2 that is X1 plus some noise
X2 = X1 + np.random.normal(0, 1, N)
X2.name = 'X2'
In[20]:
plt.plot(X1)
plt.plot(X2)
plt.xlabel('Time')
plt.ylabel('Series Value')
plt.legend([X1.name, X2.name]);

Bi v $X_2$ ch l mt chui $I(1)$ cng vi mt s nhiu tnh, nn n vn nn l $I(1)$. Hy kim tra iu ny.

In[21]:
Z = X2.diff()[1:]
Z.name = 'Z'

check_for_stationarity(Z);

p-value = 5.129595313012713e-25 The series Z is likely stationary.

Trng c v tt. By gi chng minh s ng tch hp, chng ta cn tm mt t hp tuyn tnh ca $X_1$ v $X_2$ l dng. Chng ta c th ly $X_2 - X_1$. Tt c nhng g cn li s l nhiu dng theo thit k. Hy kim tra iu ny.

In[22]:
Z = X2 - X1
Z.name = 'Z'

plt.plot(Z)
plt.xlabel('Time')
plt.ylabel('Series Value')
plt.legend(['Z']);

check_for_stationarity(Z);

p-value = 5.2026703238165325e-15 The series Z is likely stationary.

Kim tra ng tch hp

C nhiu cch kim tra ng tch hp. Bi vit trn Wikipedia ny m t mt s phng php. Ni chung, chng ta ch ang c gng tm cc h s $b_1, \dots, b_k$ to ra mt t hp tuyn tnh $I(0)$. Nu c lng tt nht cho cc h s ny khng vt qua kim tra tnh dng, th chng ta bc b gi thuyt rng tp hp l ng tch hp. iu ny s dn n nguy c v li loi II (m tnh gi), v chng ta s khng kim tra y tnh dng cho tt c cc t hp h s. Tuy nhin, li loi II thng khng vn y, v chng l an ton v khng dn n vic chng ta a ra bt k d on sai no.

Trn thc t, mt cch ph bin thc hin iu ny cho cc cp chui thi gian l s dng hi quy tuyn tnh c lng $\beta$ trong m hnh sau:

$$X_2 = \alpha + \beta X_1 + \epsilon$$

tng l nu hai bin ny ng tch hp, chng ta c th loi b s ph thuc ca $X_2$ vo $X_1$, li nhng nhiu c tnh dng. T hp $X_2 - \beta X_1 = \alpha + \epsilon$ nn l mt chui dng.

Chng ta c th thy y rng $Z$ c kh nng l chui dng (stationary) trong khong thi gian m chng ta xem xt. iu ny khin chng ta chp nhn gi thuyt rng hai ti sn ca chng ta ng tch hp (cointegrated) trong cng mt khong thi gian.

y ch l mt d on!

Hy nh rng, ging nh bt k iu g khc, bn khng nn gi nh rng v mt tp hp ti sn no vt qua bi kim tra ng tch hp trong qu kh, chng s tip tc duy tr s ng tch hp. Bn cn xc minh rng hnh vi nht qun xy ra v s dng cc k thut xc thc m hnh khc nhau nh bn s lm vi bt k m hnh no.

Mt trong nhng iu quan trng nht trong ti chnh l thc hin nhiu ln cc c lp. y, mt nh nh lng s tm nhiu cp ti sn m h gi thuyt l ng tch hp v phn b ng u s tin ca h gia chng trong cc ln cc. iu ny ch yu cu hn mt na s cp ti sn duy tr s ng tch hp chin lc hot ng. bit thm thng tin v giao dch cp, hy xem bi ging Giao dch Cp.

Th vin c sn

May mn thay, c mt s bi kim tra c xy dng sn cho vic kim tra tnh ng tch hp. Hy tham kho ti liu ca statsmodel ti y bit thm chi tit.
